OL,10,     Fsearch and find somewhere that's
OL,11,     Fjust right?
OL,12,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,13,     FAndy and Nicki Bruce try to build
OL,14,     Fan experimental flood-proof,
OL,15,     Ffloating house on an island in the
OL,16,     FRiver Thames. But building such a
OL,17,     Fcomplex design on a site with
OL,18,     Flimited access isn't easy.
